⠀⠀⠀⢿⣷⣄⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠙⠛⠛⠛⠛⠋⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⣠⣾⡿⠀⠀⠀&#x0a;
⠀⠀⠀⠈⢿⣿⣧⡀⠀⠀⠀⢸⣧⡀⠀⠀⢀⣼⡇⠀⠀⠀⢀⣼⣿⡿⠁⠀⠀⠀&#x0a;
